      contents: `Perform a deep linguistic and cultural analysis of this Dari translation: "${dariText}" derived from source: "${sourceText}". 
      Analyze it specifically within the context of Afghan-Tajik heritage, regional dialects, and Islamic linguistic tradition. Highlight why this is authentic to Afghanistan compared to Iranian Farsi.`,
      config: {
